---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | IntelliFill" description="IntelliFill Privacy Policy - How we collect, use, and protect your data.">
  <!-- Header -->
  <header class="bg-slate-900 px-4 py-6 border-b border-slate-800">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">
        <svg class="h-5 w-5" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M19 12H5M12 19l-7-7 7-7"/>
        </svg>
        Back to Home
      </a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Content -->
  <main class="bg-slate-900 px-4 py-16">
    <article class="mx-auto max-w-4xl prose prose-invert prose-slate">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white sm:text-4xl">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-400 mt-2">Last updated: January 2026</p>

      <section class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300 mt-4">
          IntelliFill collects information you provide directly, including:
        </p>
        <ul class="text-slate-300 mt-4 space-y-2 list-disc list-inside">
          <li>Account information (name, email, password)</li>
          <li>Documents you upload for processing</li>
          <li>Form data and templates you create</li>
          <li>Usage data and analytics</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mt-10">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300 mt-4">
          We use collected information to:
        </p>
        <ul class="text-slate-300 mt-4 space-y-2 list-disc list-inside">
          <li>Provide and improve our document processing services</li>
          <li>Process payments and manage subscriptions</li>
          <li>Send service updates and notifications</li>
          <li>Respond to support requests</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mt-10">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">3. Data Security</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300 mt-4">
          We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your data:
        </p>
        <ul class="text-slate-300 mt-4 space-y-2 list-disc list-inside">
          <li>All data encrypted in transit (TLS 1.3) and at rest (AES-256)</li>
          <li>Documents are processed securely and deleted after processing</li>
          <li>Regular security audits and vulnerability assessments</li>
          <li>Access controls and authentication requirements</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mt-10">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">4. Data Retention</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300 mt-4">
          We retain your data only as long as necessary to provide our services. You can request deletion of your data at any time by contacting support.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mt-10">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">5. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300 mt-4">
          We use trusted third-party services for:
        </p>
        <ul class="text-slate-300 mt-4 space-y-2 list-disc list-inside">
          <li>Payment processing (Stripe)</li>
          <li>Cloud infrastructure (Vercel, Neon)</li>
          <li>Authentication (Supabase)</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mt-10">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">6. Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300 mt-4">
          For privacy-related questions, contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@intellifill.com" class="text-primary-400 hover:text-primary-300">privacy@intellifill.com</a>
        </p>
      </section>
    </article>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
